ken","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,250],"id":"6fd0edd1-5d01-769f-04a5-eaac65a4059d","name":"Note: Pull Side A (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Pull Side B (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,790],"id":"44e4d9c3-6d66-8c33-7686-4f3e542c8613","name":"Note: Pull Side B (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Diff the Two Systems\n\nDiffs two streams by key into 4 lanes: only-in-A, same, different, only-in-B — the heart of the sync.\n\nPorts: ①→ Create Missing in Google Sheets · ②→ Count In-Sync Rows · ③→ Apply Updates to Google Sheets · ④→ Backfill into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"6f50b79e-31f9-c623-4cc1-ccfe2bee524c","name":"Note: Diff the Two Systems"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Create Missing in Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,-80],"id":"0c303e58-75cd-ae2d-1534-692aebe29152","name":"Note: Create Missing in Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Count In-Sync Rows\n\nCollapses all items into a single summary item (for counts and run stats).\n\nNext: Gather Sync Results","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,340],"id":"a5d56549-1608-bf95-0ab6-9d3f1b504dc8","name":"Note: Count In-Sync Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Apply Updates to Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,760],"id":"96c11075-6a33-9d7e-5e21-803ff219d0de","name":"Note: Apply Updates to Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Backfill into HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,1180],"id":"1a635287-5f96-3d61-bcd4-15517bf819de","name":"Note: Backfill into HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Gather Sync Results\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"a8b0a82f-9017-0940-3999-f8e0e809c416","name":"Note: Gather Sync Results"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Sort Leads Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"d14dc625-cc44-1561-0905-51900734c2db","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Leads Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"a6f8f3d3-0fed-c0c0-73b0-48560cada78c","name":"Note: Sort Leads Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty email","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"5cefb5b0-cfde-7e08-bbdc-802cb9016aa0","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty email\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"9c0c57c8-31bc-b3a9-6f5d-53e792cade5e","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty email"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"bd1982d7-f536-4adf-5ebf-daebf34ff9df","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"9dc81be1-c725-bad8-4081-1a543b69569c","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"df17ff3a-68fc-c8e9-2b78-24fce4cc3e7a","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"1b0bade2-bf21-298e-9376-f1a6550e4eea","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,1540],"id":"0936daf6-1dd8-571a-b0c4-5276cb758d84","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,1540],"id":"8ab18d8c-b03d-ef2b-17cf-12b818fe664c","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Clean company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API for Enrichment (04572)\n\n**Pattern:** Data Enrichment · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nClean company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API for Enrichment (04572). It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual enrichment is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Pull Side A (HubSpot) → Diff the Two Systems → Create Missing in Google Sheets → Gather Sync Results → Stamp Processing Time → Sort Leads Newest First → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to data enrichment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating enrichment in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"4778e06f-17d5-52d0-f136-6ff8af3db4c5","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-620],"id":"7ab6e755-fa3e-7385-a498-016450f0640c","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-620],"id":"af5d07b7-78fc-c96d-cf1d-b9f3234b9f42","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your enrichment process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-620],"id":"45ffcefb-1efc-c9a7-1e70-9875d31a8a43","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Pull Side A (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Pull Side B (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Pull Side A (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff the Two Systems","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Pull Side B (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff the Two Systems","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Diff the Two Systems":{"main":[[{"node":"Create Missing in Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Count In-Sync Rows","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Apply Updates to Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Backfill into HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Create Missing in Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Count In-Sync Rows":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Apply Updates to Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Backfill into HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Gather Sync Results":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Leads Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Leads Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty email":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"1f01bd67-2a29-408f-8471-fde640fdb50a","id":"FDX04572"}